videos.description: DeAndre Jordan rejects DeMar DeRozan at the rim, and James Harden finds Joe Harris for 3 on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jordan's denial of DeRozan sets up a Harris 3-ball) 2021/3/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan's denial of DeRozan sets up a Harris 3-ball

videos.description: Kyrie Irving fakes a pass behind his back and then lobs it over his head to DeAndre Jordan for an alley-oop.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie gets fancy on alley-oop dime to Jordan) 2021/3/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie gets fancy on alley-oop dime to Jordan

videos.description: Kyrie Irving goes into his bag to hit a contested jumper over DeMar DeRozan.

videos.headline: Kyrie drains smooth step-back jumper over DeRozan

videos.description: Nicolas Claxton makes his presence felt with two alley-oop jams in short succession.

videos.headline: Claxton flushes alley-oops on back-to-back possessions

videos.description: Lonnie Walker IV hits Dejounte Murray in stride with a long bounce pass between two Nets defenders.

videos.headline: Walker's sweet bounce pass sets up Murray for a bucket

videos.description: Kyrie Irving misses at the rim, and Dejounte Murray races the other way to hit a game-tying shot as the buzzer sounds.

videos.description: James Harden and Kyrie Irving combine to score 57 points as the Nets defeat the Spurs in overtime 124-113.
